6 was received by the Office, the applicant shall not be approved for a
7 partial abatement pursuant to this section unless the applicant
8 submits a new request pursuant to subsection 1.
9 7. If a business whose partial abatement has been approved
10 pursuant to this section and is in effect ceases:
